* Investigate\nCaching Issues
** Disk Cache
***_ Automatic for Parquet
***_ Worker SSD storage
***_ spark.databricks.io.cache.enabled
***_ Transparent caching
** Under-Caching
***_ Data re-read from storage
***_ High Input values in Spark UI
***_ Enable disk cache
***_ Use SSD worker nodes
** Over-Caching
***_ Memory consumed by cache
***_ OOM errors
***_ Memory pressure
***_ Review cache reuse
** Spark Cache
***_ .cache() or .persist()
***_ Explicit management
***_ Call .unpersist() when done
***_ Unlike disk cache: manual
@endmindmap
